<sect1 id="dir_5205709783a7211c89208e8fb92d7bc9_1autotoc_md231">
<title>HealthUpdateSystem</title><para>Processes entities with <computeroutput>HealthComponent</computeroutput> and <computeroutput>SpawnedByProfileComponent</computeroutput>:</para>
<para>1. Queries all entities with health components 2. Checks if <computeroutput>isAlive()</computeroutput> returns false 3. Issues <computeroutput>DespawnCommand</computeroutput> to return entity to pool 4. Publishes <computeroutput>DeathEvent</computeroutput> with optional <computeroutput>AttackContext</computeroutput></para>
<para>The attack context is retrieved from <computeroutput>LastAttackerComponent</computeroutput> if present.</para>
